# LifeSet Admin Dashboard

Next.js admin dashboard for managing organisations, members, bookings, and memberships.

## Setup

```bash
cd admin-dashboard
npm install
npm run dev
```

## Structure

```
admin-dashboard/
├── src/
│   ├── app/
│   │   ├── layout.tsx          # Root layout
│   │   ├── page.tsx            # Login page
│   │   └── dashboard/
│   │       ├── page.tsx        # Main dashboard
│   │       ├── schedule/       # Class schedule management
│   │       ├── members/        # Member management
│   │       ├── memberships/    # Membership management
│   │       ├── packs/          # Pack management
│   │       ├── analytics/      # Analytics dashboard
│   │       └── settings/       # Organisation settings
│   ├── components/
│   │   ├── Schedule/
│   │   ├── Members/
│   │   ├── Memberships/
│   │   └── Analytics/
│   └── lib/
│       ├── firebase-admin.ts   # Firebase Admin SDK
│       └── auth.ts             # Authentication
```

## Features

- Organisation management
- Class schedule management
- Member management
- Membership creation and management
- Pack creation and management
- Attendance tracking
- Analytics dashboard
- Stripe/GoCardless integration (future)

## Authentication

Uses Firebase Auth. Only users with `role: "admin"` or `role: "staff"` can access the dashboard.

